title: Central Statistics Office Ireland, Number of Family Units by size of family (number of persons) by town, Ireland, 2006
name: Central Statistics Office Ireland, Number of Family Units by size of family (number of persons) by town, Ireland, 2006
description: This dataset has data on Number of Family Units by size of family unit (number of persons) throughout towns in Ireland that have a population of over 1000. The data includes both number and percentages for family units of the following sizes: 2 persons, 3 persons, 4 persons, 5 persons, and 6 or more persons. The towns have been geolocated by their lat/lon position. For more info about the data go to cso.ie/census.
